.Dl BRUSH CONTAINER
.Pp
The bottom row, initially showing empty
buttons, is the brush container. You can
right-click a button to store the current
brush in it, and then whenever you need the
brush back, open this menu again and
left-click the button.
The container can memorize resizable brushes
as well as brushes grabbed from the image.
Brushes are lost when you exit the program.
.Pp
