brush that aren\(aqt the Back-color will be
set to the Fore-color. But this option
doesn\(aqt alter the brush: you\(aqll just have
to right-click on the "Get brush" buttons
to get your brush back.
.Pp
Note: When you press (not in the menu) the
paintbrush becomes the smallest member of
the "Disc" family: i.e one pixel.
